ory:Naval battles involving Great Britain]]\n[[Category:Naval battles involving France]]\n[[Category:1782 in Asia]]\n[[Category:Naval battles of the American Revolutionary War]]\n", "name_user": "Rama", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eOrder of battle", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battle_of_Sadras"}
