ace.\n\n==Results in World Golf Championships==\n''Results not in chronological order prior to 2015.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Tournament!!1999!!2000!!2001!!2002!!2003!!2004!!2005!!2006!!2007!!2008\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC-Mexico Championship|Championship]]\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T7\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T5\n|NT<sup>1</sup>\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|7\n|T12\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T4\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T3\n|T32\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T3\n|T15\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC Match Play|Match Play]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|R16\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|R16\n|R64\n|R64\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|R16\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|R32\n|R32\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC Invitational|Invitational]]\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T7\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|T58\n|T30\n|T16\n|T13\n|T22\n|T20\n|T36\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Tournament!!2009!!2010!!2011!!2012!!2013!!2014!!2015!!2016!!2017!!2018!!2019!!2020\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC-Mexico Championship|Championship]]\n|T31\n|T37\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|T60\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T3\n|T16\n|T31\n|T11\n|T12\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T7\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T6\n|T37\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC Match Play|Match Play]]\n|R64\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|4\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|R64\n|R32\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|R16\n|T34\n|T18\n|T30\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|R16\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|QF\n|NT<sup>2</sup>\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC Invitational|Invitational]]\n|T22\n|T22\n|T53\n|T29\n|T40\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|2\n|T37\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|T39\n|T39\n|T40\n|\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[WGC-HSBC Champions|Champions]]\n|T23\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\