ft|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]]\n|T22\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T7\n|T38\n|T45\n|T35\n|T18\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T5\n|T21\n|CUT\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]\n|T14\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T9\n|CUT\n|T21\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T2\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T6\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"|T5\n|T37\n|CUT\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]\n|CUT\n|T12\n|CUT\n|T61\n|T35\n|T54\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|}\n{| cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 95%; border: #aaa solid 1px; border-collapse: collapse;text-align:center;\"\n|- style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n!align=\"left\"|Tournament\n!2019\n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]\n|CUT\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]\n|CUT\n|-\n|align=left|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]]\n|T52\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]\n|T67\n|}\n{{legend|lime|Win}}\n{{legend|yellow|Top 10}}\n{{legend|#eeeeee|Did not play}}\n<span style=\"font-size:87%;\">LA</span> = Low Amateur<br>\nCUT = missed the half way cut<br>\n\"T\" = tied<br>\nDQ = disqualified\n\n===Summary===\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n!Tournament !! Wins !! 2nd !! 3rd !! Top-5 !! Top-10 !! Top-25 !! Events !! Cuts made\n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]         || 1 || 0 || 0 || 2 ||  4 ||  6 || 21 || 14\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]           || 0 || 2 || 1 || 3 ||  4 ||  6 || 21 ||  10\n|-\n|align=left|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]] || 0 || 0 || 1 || 3 ||  5 ||  11 || 20 || 17\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]      || 0 || 2 || 0 || 5 || 10 ||  12 || 23 || 18\n|-\n!Totals                                    !! 1 !! 4 !! 2 !! 13 !! 23 !! 35 !! 85 !! 59\n|}\n*Most consecutive cuts made \u2013 10 (2014 U.S. Open \u2013 2016 Open)\n*Longest streak of top-10s \u2013 4 (2002 Masters \u2013 2002 PGA)\n\n==The Players Championship==\n===Wins (1)===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year!!Championship!!54 holes!!Winning score!!Margin!!Runner-up\n|- style=\"background:#f2ecce;\