{"title_page": "Aandan Adimai", "text_new": "{{short description|2001 film by Manivannan}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2015}}\n{{More citations needed|date=September 2013}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Aandan Adimai\n| image          = \n| caption        =\n| director       = [[Manivannan]]\n| producer       = K. Dhadhakhan\n| writer         = Manivannan\n| screenplay     = \n| starring       = {{ubl|[[Sathyaraj]]|[[Suvalakshmi]]|[[Divya Unni]]}}\n| music          = [[Ilaiyaraaja]]\n| cinematography = D. Shankar\n| editing        = P. Venkateswara Rao\n| studio         = KDK International films\n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{Film date|df=y|2001|11|14}}\n| country        = India\n| runtime        = \n| language       = Tamil\n}}\n\n'''''Aandan Adimai''''' is a [[Tamil films of 2001|2001]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] [[drama film]], directed by [[Manivannan]], starring [[Sathyaraj]], [[Suvalakshmi]] and [[Divya Unni]] in lead roles. The film had a musical score by [[Ilaiyaraaja]] and was released in 2001.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbthots.com/reviews/2001/aadimai.html |title=Aandaan Adimai |publisher=Bbthots.com |date= |accessdate=2013-09-07}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n{{colbegin}}\n*[[Sathyaraj]] as Sivaraman\n*[[Suvalakshmi]] as Maheswari\n*[[Divya Unni]] as Gayathri (Voice dubbed by [[Jayageetha]] )\n*[[Ranjith (actor)|Ranjith]]\n*[[Manivannan]]\n*[[Thalaivasal Vijay]]\n*[[Vagai Chandrasekhar]]\n*[[Nizhalgal Ravi]]\n*[[Raj Kapoor (Tamil film director)|Raj Kapoor]]\n*[[Junior Balaiah]]\n*[[Periya Karuppu Thevar]]\n*[[Mayilsamy]]\n*[[Kalairani]]\n*[[Shanti Williams]]\n*[[Kamala Kamesh]]\n*Krithika as Sivaraman's sister (Debut)<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aaak_7LmEA8</ref>\n{{colend}}\n\n==Soundtrack==\nSoundtrack is composed by Ilaiyaraaja and lyrics for songs were written by Vaali, Pulamaipithan, Muthulingam, Mu. Metha and Thamarai.<ref name=\"raaga\">{{cite web | url=http://play.raaga.com/tamil/album/aandaan-adimai-T0000359 | title=Aandan Adimai&nbsp;\u2014 Tamil movie songs&nbsp;\u2014 Raaga.com | publisher=Raaga | accessdate=18 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mio.to/album/Aandaan+Adimai+%282001%29|title=Aandan Adimai songs|work=Music India Online|accessdate=5 Oct 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/aandan-adimai-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-ep/586964506?ign-mpt=uo%3D4|title=Aandan Adimai (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) - EP|work=Apple Music}}</ref>\n*Anne Anne&nbsp;\u2014 [[Shankar Mahadevan]]\n*Ennenna Paadapaduthura&nbsp;\u2014 [[Harini (singer)|Harini]], Bhavatharini\n*Undhan Rajyathil&nbsp;\u2014 Ilaiyaraja\n*Nammava&nbsp;\u2014 [[Madhu Balakrishnan]], Shanmugasundari\n*Thillu Mullu&nbsp;\u2014 Pushpavanam Kuppusamy\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Manivannan}}\n\n[[Category:2001 films]]\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2000s Tamil-language films]]\n[[Category:Tamil film scores by Ilaiyaraaja]]\n[[Category:Films directed by Manivannan]]\n\n\n{{2000s-Tamil-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2001 film by Manivannan}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2015}}\n{{More citations needed|date=September 2013}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Aandan Adimai\n| image          = \n| caption        =\n| director       = [[Manivannan]]\n| producer       = K. Dhadhakhan\n| writer         = Manivannan\n| screenplay     = \n| starring       = {{ubl|[[Sathyaraj]]|[[Suvalakshmi]]|[[Divya Unni]]}}\n| music          = [[Ilaiyaraaja]]\n| cinematography = D. Shankar\n| editing        = P. Venkateswara Rao\n| studio         = KDK International films\n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{Film date|df=y|2001|11|14}}\n| country        = India\n| runtime        = \n| language       = Tamil\n}}\n\n'''''Aandan Adimai''''' is a [[Tamil films of 2001|2001]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] [[drama film]], directed by [[Manivannan]], starring [[Sathyaraj]], [[Suvalakshmi]] and [[Divya Unni]] in lead roles. The film had a musical score by [[Ilaiyaraaja]] and was released in 2001.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbthots.com/reviews/2001/aadimai.html |title=Aandaan Adimai |publisher=Bbthots.com |date= |accessdate=2013-09-07}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n{{colbegin}}\n*[[Sathyaraj]] as Sivaraman\n*[[Suvalakshmi]] as Maheswari\n*[[Divya Unni]] as Gayathri (Voice dubbed by [[Jayageetha]] )\n*[[Ranjith (actor)|Ranjith]]\n*[[Manivannan]]\n*[[Thalaivasal Vijay]]\n*[[Vagai Chandrasekhar]]\n*[[Nizhalgal Ravi]]\n*[[Raj Kapoor (Tamil film director)|Raj Kapoor]]\n*[[Junior Balaiah]]\n*[[Periya Karuppu Thevar]]\n*[[Mayilsamy]]\n*[[Kalairani]]\n*[[Shanti Williams]]\n*[[Kamala Kamesh]]\n*Pravitha as Gayathri's friend\n{{colend}}\n\n==Soundtrack==\nSoundtrack is composed by Ilaiyaraaja and lyrics for songs were written by Vaali, Pulamaipithan, Muthulingam, Mu. Metha and Thamarai.<ref name=\"raaga\">{{cite web | url=http://play.raaga.com/tamil/album/aandaan-adimai-T0000359 | title=Aandan Adimai&nbsp;\u2014 Tamil movie songs&nbsp;\u2014 Raaga.com | publisher=Raaga | accessdate=18 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mio.to/album/Aandaan+Adimai+%282001%29|title=Aandan Adimai songs|work=Music India Online|accessdate=5 Oct 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/aandan-adimai-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-ep/586964506?ign-mpt=uo%3D4|title=Aandan Adimai (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) - EP|work=Apple Music}}</ref>\n*Anne Anne&nbsp;\u2014 [[Shankar Mahadevan]]\n*Ennenna Paadapaduthura&nbsp;\u2014 [[Harini (singer)|Harini]], Bhavatharini\n*Undhan Rajyathil&nbsp;\u2014 Ilaiyaraja\n*Nammava&nbsp;\u2014 [[Madhu Balakrishnan]], Shanmugasundari\n*Thillu Mullu&nbsp;\u2014 Pushpavanam Kuppusamy\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Manivannan}}\n\n[[Category:2001 films]]\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2000s Tamil-language films]]\